        {
            "id": "human",
            "name": "Human",
            "description": "Adaptable and ambitious. Humans thrive through sheer determination and versatility, compensating for their lack of innate magic with an unmatched capacity to learn and grow.",
            "lore": "The first settlers to bond with the Everwood, Humans arrived in Verdance generations ago and built the foundations of civilization amid the living forest. Their adaptability allowed them to navigate the complex politics of the Domain, forging alliances with the Emerald Coven and the Bloomguard alike. Most numerous in Verdance, they fill every role from soldier to scholar, their ambition tempered by the ever-present dangers of the Abyss. It is said that Humans were the first to petition the Veilkeepers for knowledge, establishing the consultation traditions that persist to this day.",
